NOTE ON DATA AND TRADEMARKS

The keyboard shortcut data in this repository consists of factual reference
information compiled from each application's official documentation (cited in
every data file via `officialDocsUrl`). Facts are not subject to copyright and
are provided for reference only.

All product names, logos, and brands are property of their respective owners.
Brand icons are sourced from the open-source Simple Icons project
(https://simpleicons.org). Use of these names, logos, and brands is for
identification purposes only and does not imply endorsement. KeyMap is an
independent project and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by
any of the applications it references.
